title: TNA Impact Wrestling Reveals Their New Logo
text:
TNA Impact Wrestling Reveals Their New Logo Matthew Mueller Start Photo Gallery Back to Article Image of 
The ongoing saga of TNA and it's constantly criticized ownership situation has finally settled down with the ouster of Dixie Carter and the incoming Anthem Sports and Entertainment. With new leadership typically comes rebranding, and it didn't take long for the first pieces of that to make their way online ( via IWNerd ). 
TNA recently held their first Impact Wrestling taping of the new year, and at the event fans and spectators were treated to a new logo for the embattled wrestling brand. While there isn't a hi-res image out there at the moment, many snapped pictures of it and posted them on social media, a few of which you can find below.
